headline: Shelf-Stable Food Stocks Q4 Results: Benchmarking J. M. Smucker (NYSE:SJM)
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at shelf-stable food stocks, starting with J. M. Smucker (NYSE:SJM).
